  <brief_title>Microenvironment of Adipose Tissue in Endocannabinoid System</brief_title>
  <official_title>Microenvironment of Adipose Tissue in Endocannabinoid System Before and After Roux-en-y Gastric Bypass Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
